#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter.md:1
msgid "Refactor the `vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter` for more modularity"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter.md:3
msgid ""
"The `vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter` now utilises a strategy pattern "
"`vtkPartitioningStrategy` for encapsulating the partitioning algorithm to "
"use when redistributing a data set. You can now change the partitioning "
"strategy dynamically at runtime."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter.md:5
msgid ""
"The previous strategy hardcoded into the `vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter` has "
"been refactored into the `vtkNativePartitioningStrategy` class (inheriting "
"from `vtkPartitioningStrategy`). No novel strategies are included in this "
"development."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter.md:7
msgid ""
"WARNING: The method `vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter::SplitDataSet` has changed "
"signature and been made private. It no longer made any sense in the generic "
"implementation proposed in this development."
msgstr ""
